<p>This type can be used for many different scenarios.
The filter is linked to the attributes, characteristics or properties in your system.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Example</em></strong>: Choose this type if you want to create the filter “Colour” or “Size”.</p>
</div></div></td>
