</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Example</em></strong>: Choose this type if you want to create the filter “Brand name”.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Availability</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>This type of filter is linked to the availabilities in your system.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Example</em></strong>: Choose this type if you want customers to filter for items that ship within 24 hours.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Price</strong></p></td>
