</table></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Position</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Where should the filter appear in the webshop?
In other words, which filter should be displayed first, second, third, etc?
Enter the position number here.</p></td>
</tr>
